Assistant Stylist / Sales consultant
M7 Bespoke
Location:
Dubai
Date: 03-05-2014
Payrate: 3,500 To 5,000 Monthly (AED)
Salary Details:
Potential for additional commission in case of upsell / cross-sell conversions.
Job Type: Employee
Job Status: Full Time, Part Time
Categories:
Retail & Wholesale
M7 Bespoke
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
Young ambitious female required for role in growing men's bespoke clothing business.  Applicant will be required to work closely with lead stylist to manage client fittings and consultations on an outdoor basis.  Key responsibilities:
-manage end-to-end fitting process with clients
-provide style advice as needed
-upsell/cross-sell as required
Requirements
Female, 21-35 years old
1-2 years experience in men's or women's fashion
Excellent eye for detail
Experience in dealing with high-profile and demanding clients
Fluent in English (and optionally Hindi)
